Patient-Reported Outcomes Measures in Cardiovascular Disease: An Evidence Map of the Psychometric Properties of Health Status Instruments. 
Given the use of PROMs to guide FDA approvals of drugs and devices in CVDs, there is a need for better adherence to quality standards in PROM validation. None.
